This project introduces the complete Docker workflow you'll use repeatedly in DevOps: create an application, package it into an image, run it as a container, verify it works, and manage the container lifecycle. Once you're comfortable with these steps, you'll be well prepared to move on to multi-container applications using Docker Compose.
